        <updateDate>2020-02-25T14:07:52Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Gold Star Spouses and Spouses of Injured Servicemembers Leasing Relief Expansion Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes spouses of military servicemembers to terminate leases of premises and motor vehicles in certain situations. Specifically, the bill allows the spouse of a servicemember lessee to terminate the leases within one year of the date on which the servicemember incurs a catastrophic injury or illness connected with their military service. </p> <p>The bill also allows the spouse of a servicemember lessee who died in military service to terminate a motor vehicle lease within one year of the death of the servicemember. </p> ]]></text>
      </summary>
